1
00:00:06,506 --> 00:00:07,607
It's not enough.

2
00:00:09,075 --> 00:00:10,243
Still not enough.

3
00:00:10,543 --> 00:00:12,045
Fine, you're impossible.

4
00:00:15,081 --> 00:00:16,161
You're so high-maintenance.

5
00:00:17,150 --> 00:00:19,319
I'm the "Little Prince" of the Bais.

6
00:00:19,719 --> 00:00:21,021
I'm supposed to be difficult.

7
00:00:23,456 --> 00:00:25,125
You really don't regret being with me?

8
00:00:26,993 --> 00:00:29,294
People will say...

9
00:00:29,295 --> 00:00:30,855
you're just after my family's money.

10
00:00:32,308 --> 00:00:33,242
And then,

11
00:00:33,267 --> 00:00:35,367
they'll dig into your past

12
00:00:35,368 --> 00:00:37,437
and say you're a social climber.

13
00:00:38,405 --> 00:00:39,372
Or worse,

14
00:00:39,373 --> 00:00:41,341
fans will come after you

15
00:00:42,208 --> 00:00:44,878
for ruining my reputation.

16
00:00:45,545 --> 00:00:47,180
Will you regret it?

17
00:00:48,348 --> 00:00:49,616
I wouldn't...

18
00:00:50,050 --> 00:00:51,051
dare.

19
00:00:54,821 --> 00:00:56,823
Is it that you don't dare,

20
00:00:57,590 --> 00:00:59,125
or that you just won't?

21
00:01:10,270 --> 00:01:11,671
This necklace...

22
00:01:12,038 --> 00:01:13,706
Why does it look so familiar?

23
00:01:20,747 --> 00:01:21,747
Stop hanging every necklace

24
00:01:21,748 --> 00:01:23,183
you find around my neck.

25
00:01:23,583 --> 00:01:25,018
I'm not a pet, you know.

26
00:01:27,620 --> 00:01:28,620
True.

27
00:01:28,848 --> 00:01:30,249
Even a pet would be more grateful.

28
00:01:30,857 --> 00:01:32,525
How am I ungrateful?

29
00:01:35,228 --> 00:01:36,763
You designed this. Forgot?

30
00:01:38,298 --> 00:01:39,466
I did?

31
00:01:40,900 --> 00:01:42,135
Wow, I'm talented.

32
00:01:44,404 --> 00:01:45,871
After the entrance exams,

33
00:01:45,872 --> 00:01:47,207
you asked what I wanted,

34
00:01:47,440 --> 00:01:48,808
so I had you draw a wing for me.

35
00:01:50,610 --> 00:01:52,712
Why did I only draw one wing?

36
00:01:53,546 --> 00:01:55,047
Because the other one is yours.

37
00:01:55,048 --> 00:01:56,181
That way,

38
00:01:56,182 --> 00:01:57,951
I'll never be able to leave you.

39
00:01:59,385 --> 00:02:00,353
Was I really

40
00:02:00,354 --> 00:02:01,521
that calculating back then?

41
00:02:03,056 --> 00:02:04,157
But tell me,

42
00:02:05,058 --> 00:02:06,225
back then,

43
00:02:06,226 --> 00:02:08,294
did you actually like me?

44
00:02:09,796 --> 00:02:10,964
You already know.

45
00:02:12,932 --> 00:02:14,667
I want to hear you say it.

46
00:02:17,370 --> 00:02:18,470
If you had confessed

47
00:02:18,471 --> 00:02:19,639
to me back then,

48
00:02:19,939 --> 00:02:21,541
I wonder if I would've said yes.

49
00:02:23,576 --> 00:02:24,110
But at that point,

50
00:02:24,111 --> 00:02:25,378
we hadn't even met in person.

51
00:02:27,714 --> 00:02:28,848
If you like someone,

52
00:02:29,382 --> 00:02:30,416
just

53
00:02:30,650 --> 00:02:31,751
go for it.
